Many, many thanks to sevenload GmbH for sponsoring the initial development of Grammatista. Check out their fantastic product and their other open source efforts at sevenload.com

The Name
--------
grammatista -ae, m. a teacher or master of grammar or languages.

Mad props to Mark for coming up with this one! See more of his genuis at mark.org.il
